{
  "stem": "13096.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The first time, you know, in the camp, by the joy, by the wind, I don't know what it was, I pass away.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know, I become unconscious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I just collapse.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Russian, I say, and everybody was, you know, so happy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Me, I collapse, the first time I collapse, you know, in the thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the poor fellow, you know, he had in his pocket-- I don't know, I still remember today, he had like cubes of sugar in his pocket and lots of almonds.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] He took all his sugar and all his almonds, he gave it to us, just, you know, to-- to-- like a gift.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He had nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he told us, you know, that try to make thing that you should go so many kilometers away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There is a camp, he explained to us, plenty Jewish, plenty soldier.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They're all Russian there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We have to be there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We should go there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So the next day-- And then, while we were in that cart, we will see clearly all the fighting, the Russian against the Allied, you know, in the snow, in the sky, all these, you know, fires, and bombs, and this, and that.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We were not even scared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We were looking in the sky.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So-- but in any case, when we heard also in the camp, the Russian is there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they are going to look after us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We didn't trust.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I say, well, maybe it must be another kind of Germans or whatever, if it has to be a camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So we won't go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We decide all of us not to go, to stay there where we are.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And that was because we can hunt plenty food by that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
